---
title: Homemade Haloumi & Courgette Fritters with Potato Wedges & Avocado Salad
description: Have fun in the kitchen, crafting delicious haloumi and veggie fritters. Roll up your sleeves and enjoy how easily this dinner comes together. A side of wedges, herby mayo for dipping and a fresh avocado salad is all you need to complete this simple yet deliciously fun meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/65948a7fb6e284551035ad0a-f83585b7.jpeg
